    "Description": "Lyrics English Translation　by DANN\n\nBlowing wind.\nShining light.\nA prayer for justice.\nTransform! Shishimaru into Lion Man. .\n\nTo save the peace of homeland Japan.\nDefeat The evil Dark Lord.\nIt's the time.  Straight away\nTransform now!\n\nRun and run, Lion man.\nFly so high, Lion man.\nHe is the sword man.\nLion-Maru.\n\nBlowing wind.\nShining light.\nA prayer of Ninja.\nTransform! Shishimaru into Lion Man. .\n\nSaori, Koske, with his families.\nOn the road to victory.\nIt's the time.  Straight away\nTransform now!\n\nShout it loud,  Lion man.\nMarcing on,  Lion man.\nHe is the sword man.\nLion-Maru.\n\nBlowing wind.\nShining light.\nThat is our prayer\nTransform! Shishimaru into Lion Man. .\nRiding the noble White Pegasus\nBrandish the sword of the king\nIt's the time.  Straight away\nTransform now!\n\nBe furious!　 Lion man.\nFight and fight! Lion man.\nHe is the sword man.\nLion-Ma-ru.",
